candy.name: Tombstone Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, they feel their skin melt to the ground in a sweet flavorful way.

candy.name: Pumpkin Fair Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, they feel the excitement and a hint of squash roll off their tongue.

candy.name: Cob Web Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, their lips feel sticky and silky.

candy.name: Hat Trick Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, the magic in the air surronds their body, making them feel powerful.

candy.name: Wormhole Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, their body feels lost and disconnected from the world.

candy.name: Cornhole Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, they feel like the embodiment of corn.

candy.name: Ghostly Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, they feel invisible and very very spooky.

candy.name: Hallowful Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, the spirit of Hallow rushes into their body, making them feel one with candy.

candy.name: Skullcore Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, their bones start to dance to festival music in the distance.

candy.name: Eye Sight Sucker
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, their eyes start to feel drained but also powerful.

candy.name: Blood Drop Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, the blood into their veins

candy.name: Candy Corn Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, they feel fluffy and hard as the same time.

candy.name: Cloudy Dream Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, the feeling of clouds brush through their skin.

candy.name: Gum Drop Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, they feel a sugar rush and now feel unusually hyper.

candy.name: Hallows Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, the spirit of Hallow rushes into their body, making them feel one with candy.

candy.name: Peppermint Surprise Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, all of a sudden, they feel a freshness of air unlike anything they've ever experience before.

candy.name: Calm Nature Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, the grass starts to grow underneath their feet. The sounds of waterfuls and distance creatures fill the land that they stand on.

candy.name: Nightmare Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, the sky turns black and they see their worst fear infront of them. Although, this may sound terrifying, atleast the taste isn't that all bitter.

candy.name: Skull Crusher Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, they feel their head being compressed by an unknown force. For some reason, it feels sour.

candy.name: Rainbow Swirl Pop
candy.description: As [name] takes a lick, they see a double rainbow in the sky and run towards. Some will never know if they return.

candy.name: Spring Waterfall Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, they feel their mouth overflow with water. The smell of spring is fumed within the water.

candy.name: Sunny Sideup Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, the sun shines brighter than usual, making their skin dry up to a crisp.

candy.name: Crystal Sparkle Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, the sky shines brighter and the oxygen becomes parent to the eye. You now understand atoms and molecules.

candy.name: Spinal Cord Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, their back tingles and starts to shift in places they didn't think it could.

candy.name: Blood Clout Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, they can feel their blood stop flowing and stay in place. The world is spinning faster and faster.

candy.name: Zombie Skin Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, their skin starts to tear into pieces as their foreskin turns green and brown all over.

candy.name: Headless Horseman Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, their suddenly pops off their body and falls on the ground. Their work is never done.

candy.name: Curse of the Living Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, they feel their well-being extend past the point of living. What they have experienced can never be expressed.

candy.name: Prime Essence Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, their souls feel enlightened and stronger. The enchantment of flavor fills their entire body.

candy.name: Werewolf Fur Wrap
candy.description: As [name] unwraps the wrapper and tosses the candy into their mouth, the hair on their skin suddenly grows thicker and longer, making them a pure werewolf.

candy.name: Dull Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth... nothing happens, its just dull and plain.

candy.name: Orange Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, citrus feels their entire body, one with the orange.

candy.name: Lime Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, their whole jaw is filled with acids and a tarty after taste.

candy.name: Strawberry Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, the jawbreaker explodes into strawberrys, overwhelming their mouth with flavor.

candy.name: Grape Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, their teeth turn into little grapes that are crushed within minutes.

candy.name: Violet Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, the night sky fills their mouth as people see stars inside.

candy.name: Blueberry Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, their tongues become flushed with blueberries. Literally the ocean swims on their tastebuds.

candy.name: Cherry Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, their tongues become flushed with cherries. Literally the ocean swims on their tastebuds.

candy.name: Grass Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, they feel themselves become one with farm animals. They also love the taste of grass.

candy.name: Vanilla Jawbreaker
candy.description: As [name] chucks the whole jawbreaker into their mouth, the sweetness of vanilla consumes their entire mouth.

candy.name: Blood Cell Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, the understand why vampires live off blood. The richness of tender flavor speaks too many words.

candy.name: Ribcage Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, each chew tickles their ribcages as it plays a song for people to hear.

candy.name: Spellcraft Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, they start to fly. Soaring through the thundering sky.

candy.name: Blob Glob Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, they realize its really hard to chew so instead they just suck in the flavors.

candy.name: Sunlight Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, light shines bright off of them. Making them practically the sun!

candy.name: Spirit Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, their spirit escapes their body. Finally free from being trapped in flesh.

candy.name: Grape Soda Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth... they spit it out. Grape Soda isn't really that good.

candy.name: Villianous Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, the world becomes a comic book. They are now a villian of this world.

candy.name: Victory Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, after all these years... they won the battle.

candy.name: Swamp Gum
candy.description: As [name] chucks the piece of gum in their mouth, mud leaks out of their mouth endlessly. Luckily they can still breathe.

candy.name: Ocean Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like clean and filtered cold water with a hint of blueberry.

candy.name: Cloud Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like fluffy pillows with a hint of marshmellow and sugar.

candy.name: Sun Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like the spicy sun with a hint of lemon.

candy.name: Grape Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like grapes with a hint of grapes and a dash of grapes. Grapes.

candy.name: Thoughtful Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like big brain juice with a hint of watermelon.

candy.name: Lava Lamp Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like charcoal and smoke with a hint of hot sauce.

candy.name: Moss Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like grass and vegan food with a hint of lime.

candy.name: Calm Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like a good sleep with a hint of cherry.

candy.name: Orange Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like orange soda. So filly.. so filling.

candy.name: Fizzy Chewy
candy.description: As [name] chucks the chewy in their mouth, each chew tastes like their favorite soda with a hint of vanilla.

candy.name: Midnight Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, everything becomes dark but calm. Like everything is finally okay.

candy.name: Sunshine Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, they become one with the light. Who needs the sun with this hallower!?

candy.name: Vegan Friendly Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, they appreciate that it is vegan friendly. Very grassy.

candy.name: Bloody Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, the blood in their veins rushes and boils. Anyone a doctor?

candy.name: Vanilla Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, the sweetness wraps around their tongue and enriches their experience.

candy.name: Bumblebee Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, they cane sticks to their tongue like rich rich honey.

candy.name: Lime Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, their tongue melts from the acid. Ouch.

candy.name: Limb Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, their limbs double joint and twist in weird places. Somehow it doesn't hurt them.

candy.name: Happy Time Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, they can't stop smiling. It is becoming really concerning.

candy.name: Quiet Flow Sugar Cane
candy.description: As [name] takes a suck on the cane, everything becomes quiet. ... ... ...

creatures.name: Blair the Witch
description: They look through the books in the endless library and find candy wedged between the pages on some of them!
Inside the dragon's chambers, they find a large pile of candy and managed to sneak out with it without waking up the dragon.
For some odd reason, they climb the house to the roof. Once there, they find candy floating and hovering. Carefully, they grab the candy and climb down.

creatures.name: Dexter the Werewolf
description: They managed to find candy next to a suspicious cave. They decided that the candy is worth the risk and stubbornly steals it.

creatures.name: Frank the Living
description: They see a colossal giant walk before they and hand they some candy!

creatures.name: Crystal the Vampire
description: Inside a large jar of blood, you spot candy inside of it. Because of their love of candy, they dive into the blood and take the candy.

creatures.name: Tom the Zombie
description: Little undead candies that don't look safe to eat spawn beside the feet of them. While no one was looking, they grab the candy and put it in a glass jar.

creatures.name: Swag
description: You grabbed one of the many floating candies in the swag dimension.
Swaggolicious Flavor is now in your grasp.

creatures.name: Dry Bones the Skeleton
description: THeY FiNd kAnDy iNsIdE Of BONES!
Did you know that bOnEs aRe kAnDy?!
Dry Bones, the once ruler of skeletons, gives them bOnEs fIlLeD WiTh kAnDy!

creatures.name: Glob the Blob
description: They see candy inside a happy blob. They decide into their best interest to stick their arm inside the blob to get the candy. The blob feel violated.
